OL,3,CMan denies murder of 24-year-old shot
OL,4,Cin Nottingham
OL,6,FA man has denied murdering a "loving,
OL,7,Fcaring" 24-year-old who was fatally
OL,8,Fshot in Nottingham.
OL,10,FCoel Tainton was found dead at a
OL,11,Fproperty in Ryeland Gardens in The
OL,12,FMeadows area of the city shortly after
OL,13,F5.30am on February 28.
OL,15,FHe was treated by paramedics but died
OL,16,Fa short time later and police
OL,17,Frecovered a shotgun within minutes of
OL,18,Fattending the scene.
OL,26,@nD@^OUoD@GO]
