PN,37102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1775049066
OL,3,CMan denies murder of 24-year-old shot
OL,4,Cin Nottingham
OL,6,FJack Preston, 34, was charged with his
OL,7,Fmurder on March 3, Nottinghamshire
OL,8,FPolice said.
OL,10,FAppearing at Nottingham Crown Court
OL,11,Fvia video-link from HMP Peterborough
OL,12,Fon Wednesday, Preston, who wore a
OL,13,Fwhite t-shirt and a green jacket for
OL,14,Fthe hearing, denied Mr Tainton's
OL,15,Fmurder.
OL,17,FHe was told he would face a three-week
OL,18,Ftrial on August 24.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1775049066
OL,3,CMan denies murder of 24-year-old shot
OL,4,Cin Nottingham
OL,6,FThe defendant, of Ryeland Gardens, sat
OL,7,Fbehind a table with his hands clasped
OL,8,Ffor the hearing in front of Judge
OL,9,FNirmal Shant KC.
OL,11,FHe spoke only to confirm his name,
OL,12,Fthat he could hear the court and to
OL,13,Fenter his plea.
OL,15,FThe judge told the defendant he must
OL,16,Fnext appear in court for a pre-trial
OL,17,Freview.
OL,19,FShe said: "Your trial is now listed on
OL,20,Fthe 24th of August.
OL,26,@{D@KOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1775049066
OL,3,CMan denies murder of 24-year-old shot
OL,4,Cin Nottingham
OL,6,F"The 10th of July is when the matter
OL,7,Fwill be reviewed to make sure your
OL,8,Ftrial is on track and ready.
OL,10,F"Your solicitors will be in contact
OL,11,Fwith you to prepare a defence
OL,12,Fstatement, where you say what you are
OL,13,Fgoing to say in your trial for your
OL,14,Fdefence.
OL,16,F"That's a document you really must
OL,17,Ffocus on.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1775049066
OL,3,CMan denies murder of 24-year-old shot
OL,4,Cin Nottingham
OL,6,F"I have no reason to believe you won't
OL,7,Fcome to your trial but if you refuse
OL,8,Fto come to court, the trial can take
OL,9,Fplace without you being there.
OL,11,F"The next hearing is the 10th of July,
OL,12,Fin the meantime, you are remanded into
OL,13,Fcustody, thank you very much."
OL,15,FIn a statement released through police
OL,16,Fafter his death, Mr Tainton's family
OL,17,Fpaid tribute to their "beloved son,
OL,18,Fbrother, nephew, cousin, grandson, and
OL,19,Ffriend to so many".
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUuD@^O]yD@WOU{D@RO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1775049066
OL,3,CMan denies murder of 24-year-old shot
OL,4,Cin Nottingham
OL,6,FThey said: "Coel was loving, caring,
OL,7,Fand fiercely protective of those he
OL,8,Fheld close. His heart was big,
OL,9,Fgenerous, and full of kindness.
OL,11,F"He had a precious soul and a
OL,12,Fcontagious laugh that could light up
OL,13,Fany room and touch everyone around him.
OL,15,F"He brought joy, warmth, and comfort
OL,16,Fto our lives in countless ways.
OL,18,F"His humour, strength, and endless
OL,19,Flove will forever remain in our hearts.
OL,26,@nD@LOUsD@AOUwD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1775049066
OL,3,CMan denies murder of 24-year-old shot
OL,4,Cin Nottingham
OL,6,F"Though words cannot express the depth
OL,7,Fof our loss, we know his love
OL,8,Fsurrounds us still.
OL,10,F"He will be so sadly missed, deeply
OL,11,Fcherished, and loved forever."
